if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('base_printer')
and type = 'U')
drop table base_printer

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: base_printer */
/*==============================================================*/
create table base_printer (
PrintrtID int identity,
Name nvarchar(10) null,
IsOnline bit null,
IsDel bit null,
DepotID int null,
AddTime datetime null,
constraint PK_BASE_PRINTER primary key (PrintrtID)
)
go
